<style type="text/css" media="screen">

.welcome_digest_email{font-family: Optima, Segoe, 'Segoe UI', Candara, Calibri, Arial, sans-serif;}
.center_text{ text-align:center; }
.left_align_text{ text-align:left; }
.email_footer{
  font-size:12px;
  text-align:center;
  opacity:0.7;
  border-top-style:solid;
	border-color:#adadad;
	border-width:thin;
  padding-top:5px;
}

h2{
	border-bottom-style:solid;
	border-color:#adadad;
	border-width:thin;
  font-size:17px;
  margin-bottom:0px;
  padding-bottom:15px;
}
h1{
  border-top-style:solid;
	border-color:#adadad;
	border-width:thin;
  font-size:15px;
  margin-bottom:0px;
  padding-bottom:0px;

}
</style>

<div class="welcome_digest_email">
  <div class="center_text">
    <br />
      <h2>Welcome to the Ski-Lines.com Email Digest!</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="left_align_text">
    <p>Hi <%= @subscriber.first_name %>,</p>
    <p>We are pretty excited that you have subscribed to our email digest! We think this will be a great way for you to
    stay engaged in one of the best sports in the World!</p>
    <p>We typically send one digest every Monday, but this could vary depending on what's happening in the ski World.
    For example, if there is a big story that you must know about, we will update you. However, if there's
    nothing too exciting happening&#8212;as the case may be in the middle of June&#8212;we will keep our emails to a minimum. </p>
    <p>As always, feel free to get in touch by emailing info@ski-lines.com. If you have any comments or suggestions, we'd love to hear from you!</p>
    <p>All the best,</p>
    <p>The Ski-Lines Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="email_footer">
    <p><i>We are doing our best to ensure that you stay more connected with the sport that you love!</i></p>
    <%= link_to "Ski-Lines.com", root_url %><br />
    <%= link_to "Edit Subscription Settings", :controller => "email_digests", :action => "edit",
:only_path => false, :id => @subscriber.id, :host => "ski-lines.com" %><br />

  </div>


</div>
